                <pre><code>${u"""
GET /api/1/graph?variable=zone_apl HTTP/1.1
Host: api.openfisca.fr
                 """.strip()}</code></pre>
                <p>Réponse :</p>
                <pre><code>${u"""
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8
                """.strip()}</code></pre>

